\q2 and from the fields of Gomorrah;
\q1 their grapes are grapes of \x + \xo 32:32 \xt ch. 29:18\x*poison;
\q2 their clusters are bitter;
\q1
\v 33 their wine is the poison of \x + \xo 32:33 \xt Job 20:14, 16; Ps. 58:4 (Heb.)\x*serpents
\q2 and the cruel venom of asps.
\b
\q1
\v 34 “‘Is not this laid up in store with me,
\q2 \x + \xo 32:34 \xt [Job 14:17; Hos. 13:12; Rom. 2:5]\x*sealed up in my treasuries?
\q1
\v 35 \x + \xo 32:35 \xt Ps. 94:1; Isa. 1:24; 59:18; Nah. 1:2; Cited Rom. 12:19; Heb. 10:30 \x*Vengeance is mine, and recompense,\f + \fr 32:35 \ft Septuagint \fq and I will repay\f*
\q2 \x + \xo 32:35 \xt [Ps. 94:18] \x*for the time when their foot shall slip;
\q1 for \x + \xo 32:35 \xt [2 Pet. 2:3]\x*the day of their calamity is at hand,
